{"tid":1854720,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"呢世人真係好唔開心","createTime":"2020-01-31T15:46:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-31T16:02:28.000Z","uid":58316,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6a901b466c26d2fa8554a6305d27bce54425b977","tid":1854720,"uid":58316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T15:46:57.000Z","msg":"頭先買茶飲<br />\nd店員全部中學生黎<br />\n自己就大過佢地<br />\n大好多<br />\n咁多年黎<br />\n自己做咁多<br />\n唔敢講好努力<br />\n廢寢忘餐個隻<br />\n但就估唔到係今日結局<br />\n又可以點<br />\n呢個世界<br />\n人只可以自己一個<br />\n人就係咁<br />\n無聲無息<br />\n行完呢趟旅程<br />\n有時係街<br />\n無端端有條友<br />\n噴住煙行過<br />\n除左無奈<br />\n又可以點<br />\n其實人生好多野都係咁<br />\n你用個心做人<br />\n其實未必有用<br />\n個世界無情<br />\n你都係收皮<br />\n今生今世真係好唔開心<br />\n曾經以為<br />\n要自愛<br />\n冇人錫自己咪自己錫自己<br />\n可惜都係自欺欺人<br />\n所以已經心淡<br />\n人大左就學識凡事都睇淡<br />\n或者應該講係被迫"},{"pid":"86e23dfacd37b165bd8ce38a533cdab503963360","tid":1854720,"uid":65638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T15:55:42.000Z","msg":"Ching 有無睇下相算下命，睇下點解會甘"},{"pid":"4cac14861e3dbd98a39ec09f138e0e6494966dbc","tid":1854720,"uid":221647,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T15:55:46.000Z","msg":"不需執著<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=95&amp;v=LyVAEphpUDM&amp;feature=emb_title\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Ftime_continue%3D95%26v%3DLyVAEphpUDM%26feature%3Demb_title&d=6xH2G4nGFyEJ53rX7DpuMY6aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=db8fead1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=95&amp;v=LyVAEphpUDM&amp;feature=emb_title</a>"},{"pid":"c8ae90cb64f2927a218958d6101157b026ca2e56","tid":1854720,"uid":76404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T15:56:21.000Z","msg":"我明喎"},{"pid":"5708e93289f95b07b4d8c5d4896f328a710b24e8","tid":1854720,"uid":69975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T15:57:07.000Z","msg":"或者可以諗下自己想要嘅係咩？<br />\n而唔係單純過日子為左養家搵錢咁？玩下運動去下唔同地方，就算遠嘅去唔到，香港都有好多地方值得去架，歷史建築有自然風景都有，就嘗試多到感受多啲，唔好戶外活動嘅都可以搵啲工作坊/其他興趣學下，都有機會接觸到人可以搵到朋友啊。正因為一世人唔長，就算幾理想幾拼搏都帶唔走，更加要照顧自己感受多啲，好好利用啲時間去生活而唔係生存，加油"},{"pid":"3f488ccd4c93e546d8ca8a537f174aac29b31e1f","tid":1854720,"uid":174914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T15:58:23.000Z","msg":"加油，好多同路人"},{"pid":"00556c88a5e63d0adf09e5d4c1168e5d2afd598c","tid":1854720,"uid":35106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T16:00:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67e4d6a7f3b5612ed9738c9e5e9090bce3a30025","tid":1854720,"uid":276658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T16:02:08.000Z","msg":"加油，好多同路人<br />\n捱過今次可能有新睇法"},{"pid":"e21bde81ae8155349b8b56ab1f2279288bffc68a","tid":1854720,"uid":88723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T16:02:28.000Z","msg":"咪當上一世做富豪食左世身人血饅頭 <br />\n窮奢極侈 享盡榮華富貴<br />\n今世咪還債<br />\n你有開心過既只不過你唔記得姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n正常還債應該比而家慘十倍<br />\n你而家算好好㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唯有繼續自欺欺人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}